    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly representing the pinnacle of automotive care. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, showroom-quality shine with no scratches, dents, or chips. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, with the leather upholstery and trim looking as though they just left the factory. Every mechanical and electronic feature functions perfectly, and the engine bay is exceptionally clean, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been kept in climate-controlled storage and treated with the utmost respect.",
