    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly entry into a great model? This car is ready for a new lease on life! While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic foundation for any DIY enthusiast or restorer. It's a rare opportunity to own this style at a fraction of the cost\u2014bring your tools and your vision to bring this diamond in the rough back to its former glory!",
